value.0: Hyper and playful, Claisi excitedly meets anyone who comes to visit the little den.
Tall and strong, Faith is the youngest of the breeding females. She watches over her pups with a dangerously protective stance.
This young pup seems to have developed a constant itch just above his eye.
A sloppy, wet tongue lolls out of Jediun's mouth as he almost constantly hounds the other wolves for food.
